{
  "stem": "5639.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in 1935, they had a child.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In those times, they say that you shouldn't have children after 30, that the time for childbearing finish was 25 or 26.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the child that was born was a very beautiful girl.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course it was all right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it's only the attitude has changed, but nature hasn't changed very much.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She wasn't helped by nature.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She just naturally had the child, but she was what was already later than usual.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like marriageable age-- was-- she married-- she must have married at the age of 30-- was considered already late.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think she was 32.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she was a little bit concerned that I might feel demoted.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my mother went with her to a larger town, neighboring town, [NON-ENGLISH], which had the Jewish hospital.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And her being a doctor, had the special conveniences there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My aunt.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was a dental surgeon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother stayed with her for two weeks, non-stop.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was allowed to visit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And on my first visit, my aunt said, this child of mine will be looked after by you when I will be too old to look after her.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I leave her in your care.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You will take her to her first ball.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You will be listening to her first romantic confessions.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was absolutely genuine, but at the same time she left me a legacy to look after that child.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, definitely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not only she didn't demote me, but she promoted me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she-- in a way, she burdened me with that responsibility.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I will come to it because I actually saved the child's life during the war, and I consider that-- so did everybody, but particular me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I consider that this is absolutely my--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--my responsibility.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
